            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-99e28d6f-aa5e-4751-aea6-97e20c979b82" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
